#: ../../modules/core/core_variables_parameters.rst:13
msgid ""
"Domain: Specifies the variable type, one of "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.REAL`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.INTEGER`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.POSITIVE_INTEGER`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.BINARY`, or "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.SPIN`."
msgstr ""
"Dominio: Especifica el tipo de variable, uno de "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.REAL`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.INTEGER`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.POSITIVE_INTEGER`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.BINARY`, o "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.SPIN`."

#: ../../modules/core/core_variables_parameters.rst:14
msgid "Bounds: Defines the allowed value range of the variable."
msgstr "Límites: Define el rango de valores permitidos de la variable."

#: ../../modules/core/core_variables_parameters.rst:15
msgid ""
"Encoding: Specifies how the variable is represented using binary "
"encodings, one of: :class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Bitwise`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.DomainWall`, or "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.OneHot`."
msgstr ""
"Codificación: Especifica cómo se representa la variable mediante "
"codificaciones binarias, una de: :class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Bitwise`, "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.DomainWall`, o "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.OneHot`."

#: ../../modules/core/core_variables_parameters.rst:16
msgid ""
"Precision: Applicable to :class:`Domain.REAL "
"<qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.REAL>` domain; defines the resolution "
"(e.g., floating-point precision)."
msgstr ""
"Precisión: Aplicable al dominio :class:`Domain.REAL "
"<qilisdk.core.variables.Domain.REAL>`; define la resolución "
"(p. ej., precisión de punto flotante)."

